{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845546045,"sessionID":"ses_2875b9d6bffeGTD5zIwxm1VyhX","part":{"id":"prt_d78a48f62001nklqimUXCpEl5K","messageID":"msg_d78a476cb00113M5aAIwhhi1vJ","sessionID":"ses_2875b9d6bffeGTD5zIwxm1VyhX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 Notes\n2: \n3: ## Research Notes\n4: \n5: *To be filled during implementation*\n6: \n7: ### Framework Comparison\n8: \n9: | Framework | Pros | Cons |\n10: |-----------|------|------|\n11: | Gin | Fast, popular, middleware support | External dependency |\n12: | Chi | Lightweight, std lib compatible | Less features than Gin |\n13: | std lib | No deps, standard | More boilerplate |\n14: \n15: ### References\n16: \n17: - [Go HTTP Server Patterns](https://go.dev/doc/articles/wiki/)\n18: - [Graceful Shutdown](https://go.dev/blog/graceful-server-shutdown)\n19: \n20: ## Implementation Notes\n21: \n22: *To be filled during development*\n23: \n24: ## Design Decisions\n25: \n26: *To be recorded during implementation*\n27: \n28: ## Blockers/Issues\n29: \n30: *To be tracked*\n31: \n32: ## Follow-up Items\n33: \n34: *To be added as discovered*\n\n(End of file - total 34 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 Notes\n\n## Research Notes\n\n*To be filled during implementation*\n\n### Framework Comparison\n\n| Framework | Pros | Cons |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| Gin | Fast, popular, middleware support | External dependency |\n| Chi | Lightweight, std lib compatible | Less features than Gin |\n| std lib | No deps, standard | More boilerplate |\n\n### References\n\n- [Go HTTP Server Patterns](https://go.dev/doc/articles/wiki/)\n- [Graceful Shutdown](https://go.dev/blog/graceful-server-shutdown)\n\n## Implementation Notes","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-004/notes.md","time":{"start":1775845546013,"end":1775845546043}}}}
