{"type":"text","timestamp":1775845654629,"sessionID":"ses_2875b9d6bffeGTD5zIwxm1VyhX","part":{"id":"prt_d78a5bf06001KLjG0oMgpU3oQq","messageID":"msg_d78a55bb5001LG8bpWo3cV1j19","sessionID":"ses_2875b9d6bffeGTD5zIwxm1VyhX","type":"text","text":"Based on my comprehensive examination of the codebase, here is the **Archive Summary** for AR-004:\n\n---\n\n## AR-004 Archive Summary: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\n\n### ✅ What Was Completed (Foundation Layer - ~40% of planned scope)\n\n| Category | Files Implemented | Description |\n|----------|------------------|-------------|\n| **Configuration** | `config/config.go` | Server config with 12 fields (host, port, timeouts, CORS, metrics) |\n| **Error Handling** | `errors/errors.go` | HTTPError type with 10 error constructors + MapServiceError() |\n| **Request DTOs** | `types/request.go` | CreateWorkloadRequest, UpdateWorkloadRequest, ListWorkloadsRequest, WatchOptions |\n| **Response DTOs** | `types/response.go` | Response wrapper, WorkloadResponse, ListWorkloadsResponse, HealthResponse, HealthCheck |\n| **Service Interface** | `service/service.go` | WorkloadService interface with 6 methods (Create, Get, List, Update, Delete, Watch) |\n| **Middleware Chain** | `middleware/middleware.go` | Middleware type + Chain() + Apply() functions |\n| **Request ID Middleware** | `middleware/requestid.go` | UUID generation, context propagation, X-Request-ID header |\n| **Logging Middleware** | `middleware/logging.go` | Request/response logging with duration, status, requestID |\n| **Recovery Middleware** | `middleware/recovery.go` | Panic recovery with stack trace logging + 500 response |\n| **Timeout Middleware** | `middleware/timeout.go` | Context deadline with 504 Gateway Timeout response |\n| **CORS Middleware** | `middleware/cors.go` | Origin whitelist, preflight handling, standard headers |\n\n### ⏸️ What Was Deferred (Server & Handler Layer - ~60% of planned scope)\n\n| Category | Missing Components | Tasks Affected |\n|----------|-------------------|----------------|\n| **HTTP Server** | `server/server.go`, `server/options.go` | Task 12, 13 - Server bootstrap, lifecycle, graceful shutdown |\n| **Router** | `server/router.go` | Task 14 - Route registration, chi.Mux setup, 9 API endpoints |\n| **Handlers** | Entire `handlers/` directory | Tasks 15-23 - Base handler, workload CRUD, health, metrics, SSE watch |\n| **Service Implementation** | `service/workload.go` | Task 24 - Business logic, K8s client integration |\n| **Type Conversions** | `types/workload.go` | Task 25 - DTO ↔ CRD conversion utilities |\n| **Tests** | All `*_test.go` files | Tasks 26-29 - Unit tests, integration tests |\n| **Documentation** | `doc.go` files | Task 30 - Package documentation |\n\n### 📊 Progress Metrics\n\n| Metric | Target | Completed |\n|--------|--------|-----------|\n| Files | 30 | 11 |\n| Tasks | 30 | 11 |\n| API Endpoints | 11 | 0 |\n| Test Coverage | 80% | 0% |\n\n### 🎯 Key Design Decisions (Implemented)\n\n1. **Router Choice**: Chi (documented, not implemented) - standard lib compatible, lightweight\n2. **Watch Protocol**: Server-Sent Events (SSE) - simpler than WebSocket\n3. **Response Format**: Standard wrapper with `success`, `data`, `error`, `requestId`, `timestamp`\n4. **JSON Naming**: camelCase for API fields\n5. **Error Codes**: Machine-readable codes (NOT_FOUND, VALIDATION_FAILED, etc.)\n\n### 📁 File Structure Status\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── server/\n│   └── middleware/        ✅ 6 middleware files\n│       ├── middleware.go\n│       ├── requestid.go\n│       ├── logging.go\n│       ├── recovery.go\n│       ├── timeout.go\n│       └── cors.go\n│   ├── server.go          ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n│   ├── router.go          ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n│   └── options.go         ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n├── handlers/              ❌ DIRECTORY NOT CREATED\n├── service/\n│   ├── service.go         ✅ Interface definition\n│   └── workload.go        ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n├── types/\n│   ├── request.go         ✅ Request DTOs\n│   ├── response.go        ✅ Response DTOs\n│   └── workload.go        ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n├── config/\n│   └── config.go          ✅ Configuration\n└── errors/\n    └── errors.go          ✅ Error types\n```\n\n### 📝 Next Steps for Future Pickup\n\nTo complete AR-004, the next developer should:\n\n1. **Priority 1**: Implement `server/server.go` with graceful shutdown\n2. **Priority 2**: Implement `server/router.go` with chi.Mux and route registration\n3. **Priority 3**: Create `handlers/` with base utilities and workload CRUD\n4. **Priority 4**: Implement service layer with fake K8s clientset\n5. **Priority 5**: Add comprehensive unit and integration tests\n\n---\n\n**Status**: ST-3 (Foundation) completed, ST-4 (Server) and ST-5 (Handlers) deferred to future sprint.","time":{"start":1775845654626,"end":1775845654626}}}
